---
import AboutMeImg from '../img/about/CezarArvelo_Headshot_hover.webp';
---

<section>
  <div class='container about-section'>
    <div class='about-section-img slide-in'>
      <img src={AboutMeImg} alt='' />
    </div>

    <div class='about-section-text'>
      <h2 class='about-section-title slide-in'>about</h2>
      <h3 class='about-section-subtitle slide-in'>cezar arvelo</h3>

      <h2 class='about-section-heading slide-in'>
        "Start where you are, Go where you are not"
      </h2>

      <p class='about-section-desc slide-in'>
        Over the last 10 years I've helped countless individuals and companies
        of all sizes match their brand aesthetic to their message and purpose.In
        today's day and age,you can't get by with a good product alone,but
        rather,a captivating story needs to be told through your brand.This
        visual associated with that story should embody the message you want to
        convey.This presentation was curated to showcase the depth and breadth
        of my logo and branding design work over the last decade.It has been an
        honor helping businesses make their mark through great design and I can
        only hope that the next 10 years of my contributions will positively
        impact the world.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 3fr;
    align-items: flex-start;
    column-gap: 2rem;

    padding-top: 4rem;
  }

  .about-section-img {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .about-section-img > img {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 400px;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    object-fit: contain;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: filter 0.15s ease-in-out;
  }

  .about-section-img > img:hover {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  .about-section-title {
    font-family: var(--suprtall);
    font-size: 8rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-section-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--usiversltsdLight);
    font-size: 2rem;
    letter-spacing: 5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-section-heading {
    font-family: var(--suprtall);
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .about-section-desc {
    font-family: var(--usiversltsd);
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 70ch;
  }

  /* 1180px */
  @media (max-width: 1180px) {
    .about-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      row-gap: 2rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      width: 80%;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }

  /* 1024 */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .about-section {
      column-gap: 1rem;
    }

    .about-section-heading {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-section-desc {
      max-width: 55ch;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 400px) {
    .about-section {
      width: 90%;
    }
  }
</style>
